This paper discusses the update strength parameter in probabilistic model-building GAs, which is a topic related to optimization and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper also discusses the trade-off between exploitation and exploration, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data mining (cs.DM). The analysis of the expected runtime also involves mathematical and statistical techniques, which are relevant to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS).
